 "国粹国粹， user data 丢了， firefox 你真行。我乖乖滚回 chrome", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1074017", "created": 1726721643, "deleted": 0, "content": "上午 firefox 自动更新到了 130.0.1 ，然后所有的 user data 就消失了。\r\n\r\n没错，是消失了。当前再用的 profile 下的所有文件的修改时间都是今天上午，也即它是把 profile 中文件删了后新建的。\r\n\r\n打开，一个全新的浏览器，心在滴血，脑子里全是国粹。\r\n\r\n最后补充下，我是通过 scoop 安装的 firefox ，在 prof 后 ile manager 中把 default 删了，只保留了 scoop 的 profile 。这么做的原因是之前 update 后，任务栏的 icon 需要重新 pin 。我推测是删除 default 的操作导致的。\r\n\r\n惨痛经历，各位 bro 引以为戒。", "content_rendered": "<p>上午 firefox 自动更新到了 130.0.1 ，然后所有的 user data 就消失了。</p>\n<p>没错，是消失了。当前再用的 profile 下的所有文件的修改时间都是今天上午，也即它是把 profile 中文件删了后新建的。</p>\n<p>打开，一个全新的浏览器，心在滴血，脑子里全是国粹。</p>\n<p>最后补充下，我是通过 scoop 安装的 firefox ，在 prof 后 ile manager 中把 default 删了，只保留了 scoop 的 profile 。这么做的原因是之前 update 后，任务栏的 icon 需要重新 pin 。我推测是删除 default 的操作导致的。</p>\n<p>惨痛经历，各位 bro 引以为戒。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1726721643, "replies": 79, "id": 1074017}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_large.png?m=1630576706", "name": "invest", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_normal.png?m=1630576706", "title": "投资", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/invest", "topics": 1770, "footer": "", "header": "Can you make money with money?", "title_alternative": "Invest", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_mini.png?m=1630576706", "stars": 2919, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 171, "parent_node_name": "money"}, "member": {"id": 679539, "username": "aolifu", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/aolifu", "website": "https://www.aolifu.org", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "https://www.aolifu.org", "bio": "https://www.aolifu.org", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/314a/5056/679539_mini.png?m=1718675846", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/314a/5056/679539_normal.png?m=1718675846", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/314a/5056/679539_large.png?m=1718675846", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/314a/5056/679539_xlarge.png?m=1718675846", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/314a/5056/679539_xlarge.png?m=1718675846", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/314a/5056/679539_xlarge.png?m=1718675846", "created": 1709979497, "last_modified": 1718675846}, "last_reply_by": "NDHT", "last_touched": 1726761972, "title": "美联储降息 50 个基点，是否会影响 A 股走势？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1073902", "created": 1726706142, "deleted": 0, "content": "今天 A 股会不会全线大涨？", "content_rendered": "<p>今天 A 股会不会全线大涨？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1726707643, "replies": 69, "id": 1073902}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 6334, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785", "stars": 1517, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 370220, "username": "zy445566", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/zy445566", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "zy445566", "btc": "", "location": "杭州", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7cd2/2c58/370220_mini.png?m=1575981411", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7cd2/2c58/370220_normal.png?m=1575981411", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7cd2/2c58/370220_large.png?m=1575981411", "created": 1544693697, "last_modified": 1575981411}, "last_reply_by": "her999", "last_touched": 1726761805, "title": "[求助]家里遇到老鼠了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1073925", "created": 1726710567, "deleted": 0, "content": "一开始在阳台打死一只小老鼠，以为没事了就睡觉了。\r\n\r\n但马上老鼠又来了，于是买了捕鼠神器(老鼠笼),上面还盖了个旧毛巾，结果老鼠在旧毛巾上拉屎就是不进去(感觉有嘲讽意味(就这想抓老子？))\r\n\r\n最近想尽了办法，比如带油的气球桶，老鼠夹，沾鼠板，无一例外放了之后都会在旁边拉屎就是不进去，我感觉这老鼠有点桀骜，喜欢嘲讽捕鼠工具。\r\n\r\n现在好了，这些东西它玩腻了，全家都是它拉的粑粑，感觉不止一只，是一窝。我之前打死的估计是鼠儿子，现在这窝老鼠特别猖狂，桌子上都是它的脚印。\r\n\r\n该封的洞不是用铁丝网就是用水泥封死了，想不到其它地方了。\r\n\r\n看捕鼠说明书上说老鼠相当于人类 7 到 8 岁的智商，一开始不信，现在信了。\r\n\r\n实在没办法了，大家给点思路。不现实的就算了(比如找猫，这种没资源，不知道去哪搞)", "content_rendered": "<p>一开始在阳台打死一只小老鼠，以为没事了就睡觉了。</p>\n<p>但马上老鼠又来了，于是买了捕鼠神器(老鼠笼),上面还盖了个旧毛巾，结果老鼠在旧毛巾上拉屎就是不进去(感觉有嘲讽意味(就这想抓老子？))</p>\n<p>最近想尽了办法，比如带油的气球桶，老鼠夹，沾鼠板，无一例外放了之后都会在旁边拉屎就是不进去，我感觉这老鼠有点桀骜，喜欢嘲讽捕鼠工具。</p>\n<p>现在好了，这些东西它玩腻了，全家都是它拉的粑粑，感觉不止一只，是一窝。我之前打死的估计是鼠儿子，现在这窝老鼠特别猖狂，桌子上都是它的脚印。</p>\n<p>该封的洞不是用铁丝网就是用水泥封死了，想不到其它地方了。</p>\n<p>看捕鼠说明书上说老鼠相当于人类 7 到 8 岁的智商，一开始不信，现在信了。</p>\n<p>实在没办法了，大家给点思路。不现实的就算了(比如找猫，这种没资源，不知道去哪搞)</p>\n", "last_modified": 1726711500, "replies": 68, "id": 1073925}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 223206, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 4237, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 588155, "username": "coderwei", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/coderwei", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9f48/76ac/588155_mini.png?m=1691510428", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9f48/76ac/588155_normal.png?m=1691510428", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9f48/76ac/588155_large.png?m=1691510428", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9f48/76ac/588155_xlarge.png?m=1691510428", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9f48/76ac/588155_xlarge.png?m=1691510428", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9f48/76ac/588155_xlarge.png?m=1691510428", "created": 1657874107, "last_modified": 1691510428}, "last_reply_by": "7gugu", "last_touch